longBusinessSummary: Qben Infra AB (publ) engages in the infrastructure business in the Nordics. The company undertakes railway, energy infrastructure, telecommunication, electrification, construction and civil engineering, industrial building, and real estate projects. It also provides testing, inspection, and certification services for infrastructure and industrial assets. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Hägersten, Sweden. Qben Infra AB (publ) operates as a subsidiary of Rsg Stockholm Ab.
